[It is difficult to know what the etiology of this disease might be
given the information in this article. ProMED requests further
detailed information about this illness and what the term malarial
typhoid denotes to the local health care providers there. The severe
joint pain raises the possibility of infection with chikungunya virus.

An interactive map of the Imphal area that also shows its location in
far northeast India can be accessed at:
<http://www.maplandia.com/india/manipur/imphal/> - Mod.TY

We have no idea what malarial typhoid means. - Mod.DK]
